title: Fix SE difference for Student's t-test
body: SE difference for Student's t-test was based on SE difference for Welch's t-test. Added definition for SE difference for Student's t-test based on the pooled variances (`sediffSTUD`). Thereby, replacing `pooledSD` by `pooledVAR` for clarity and changed definition of Cohen's d accordingly.
